+
+The website should feel like the beginning of a decades-long public institution, not a startup.
+
+# Brand Personality
+
+Describe the personality.
+
+Examples:
+
+- thoughtful
+- precise
+- engineering-first
+- calm
+- durable
+- transparent
+- ambitious without being loud
